  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/552473f65312419e7d8213f6fc08e359.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/552473f65312419e7d8213f6fc08e359.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/552473f65312419e7d8213f6fc08e359.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wish List</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you tired of the same old games? Then it's time to shake things up with our rooster tale game. Trust me, once you add it to your wishlist, you’ll be crowing with joy. (Get it? Because it's a rooster game...) So what are you waiting for? Go ahead and give it a try!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/8d83e9a0b06a80d6c4685b8a2f83de5d.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/8d83e9a0b06a80d6c4685b8a2f83de5d.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/8d83e9a0b06a80d6c4685b8a2f83de5d.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In our 2D platformer game, players take on the role of a brave rooster on a mission to rescue chickens that have been kidnapped by a sly fox and hidden in various locations. Players must use their wits and platforming skills to overcome challenging obstacles, outsmart the fox's traps, and save the chickens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/9e0605656b89905ca17f7a7fb3176ba5.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/9e0605656b89905ca17f7a7fb3176ba5.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/9e0605656b89905ca17f7a7fb3176ba5.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With pixel graphics and a retro aesthetic, our game offers a unique blend of adventure, puzzle-solving, and action. Players will need quick reflexes and strategic thinking to survive the fox’s various traps and hazards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/a3e89ebe1bbfb425fdc8cb3d6f062048.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/a3e89ebe1bbfb425fdc8cb3d6f062048.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/a3e89ebe1bbfb425fdc8cb3d6f062048.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Filled with cute characters and challenging levels, our game is a must-play for fans of indie, adventure, and puzzle platformers. Whether you're a seasoned platformer veteran or a newcomer to the genre, you’ll find plenty of excitement and challenge in our game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/0c1e68f70b9a42c301c2a11493987426.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/0c1e68f70b9a42c301c2a11493987426.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/0c1e68f70b9a42c301c2a11493987426.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the rooster on his quest to save the chickens and prove that even the smallest hero can triumph against impossible odds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/f7439b856b0a0e070f1ae08af8f58a90.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/f7439b856b0a0e070f1ae08af8f58a90.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/f7439b856b0a0e070f1ae08af8f58a90.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Difficulty:</strong> This game will likely be challenging and require players to use their skills and strategies to overcome obstacles and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adventure:</strong> Players will embark on a thrilling adventure to rescue chickens and take down the sly fox.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzle:</strong> The game may contain puzzles that players must solve in order to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Action:</strong> Players will engage in fast-paced action, running, jumping, and fighting their way through the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Side Scroller:</strong> The game will have a side-scrolling format, with players moving from left to right across the screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro:</strong> The pixel art style of the game will give it a nostalgic, retro feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Platformer:</strong> The game is a platformer, with players jumping and running across platforms to reach their goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategy:</strong> Players will need to use strategy and planning to successfully rescue the chickens and defeat the fox's defenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge:</strong> The game will present a series of challenges that players must overcome in order to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jump:</strong> Players will need to jump to avoid obstacles and reach high platforms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run:</strong> Players will need to run quickly to escape from enemies and navigate through levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/c3dda2e125679347940a8804ac82dfe5.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/c3dda2e125679347940a8804ac82dfe5.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/c3dda2e125679347940a8804ac82dfe5.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once upon a time, in a far-off land, there was a brave rooster who lived on a farm with his flock of chickens. However, a sly fox began to steal the chickens one by one, whisking them away to hidden locations. Determined to rescue his chickens, the rooster embarked on a perilous journey to track down the fox. Along the way, the rooster discovered he had the ability to shoot fire from his beak, which he used to fight off the fox’s traps and free the chickens. Eventually, the rooster reached the fox’s stronghold and engaged in a fierce battle. Despite facing many challenges and obstacles, the rooster never lost hope and ultimately emerged victorious, defeating the fox and rescuing the last of his chickens. The rooster returned home a hero, and the chickens lived happily ever after, safe and sound thanks to their brave protector. The end.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2f84d95c09edc6f4d8cde3e850696bf0.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2f84d95c09edc6f4d8cde3e850696bf0.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2f84d95c09edc6f4d8cde3e850696bf0.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Developer Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a solo indie game developer, creating my first game, <i>Rooster Tale</i>, has been a challenging but incredibly rewarding experience. The game follows the adventures of a rooster as he navigates through various levels filled with obstacles and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/726117ed1a43f5f54b89d85b3cc06008.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/726117ed1a43f5f54b89d85b3cc06008.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/726117ed1a43f5f54b89d85b3cc06008.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I wanted the game to have a retro feel, so I chose pixel graphics and incorporated elements of adventure and puzzle platforming. Making the game challenging is also important to me, so I’ve spent a lot of time playtesting and fine-tuning the difficulty to get it just right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2298436ea6b8b19e7012a8ae3e789f07.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2298436ea6b8b19e7012a8ae3e789f07.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2298436ea6b8b19e7012a8ae3e789f07.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The process of developing <i>Rooster Tale</i> has had its obstacles. There have been many late nights spent coding and troubleshooting, as well as moments of self-doubt where I questioned whether I could see the project through to the end. However, the sense of accomplishment I will feel when I finally finish and publish the game will be worth all the hard work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/4a3246e92be365d85af32e6ccc4c3a8d.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/4a3246e92be365d85af32e6ccc4c3a8d.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/4a3246e92be365d85af32e6ccc4c3a8d.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The process of developing <i>Rooster Tale</i> has had its obstacles. There have been many late nights spent coding and troubleshooting, as well as moments of self-doubt where I questioned whether I could see the project through to the end. However, the sense of accomplishment I will feel when I finally finish and publish the game will be worth all the hard work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/6b1b708856172f7ea2ec8a15aff570d6.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/6b1b708856172f7ea2ec8a15aff570d6.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/6b1b708856172f7ea2ec8a15aff570d6.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/ad438895147abe6b756d5542319ed5f0.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/ad438895147abe6b756d5542319ed5f0.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/ad438895147abe6b756d5542319ed5f0.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/5393edf0f087c732e836303dea851e8c.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/5393edf0f087c732e836303dea851e8c.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/5393edf0f087c732e836303dea851e8c.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/9e09586c912eb7d9df7b755071483095.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/9e09586c912eb7d9df7b755071483095.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/9e09586c912eb7d9df7b755071483095.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/8e8489a0077f2be9531920d02e930eb3.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/8e8489a0077f2be9531920d02e930eb3.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/8e8489a0077f2be9531920d02e930eb3.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/552473f65312419e7d8213f6fc08e359.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/552473f65312419e7d8213f6fc08e359.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/552473f65312419e7d8213f6fc08e359.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wish List</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you tired of the same old games? Then it's time to shake things up with our rooster tale game. Trust me, once you add it to your wishlist, you’ll be crowing with joy. (Get it? Because it's a rooster game...) So what are you waiting for? Go ahead and give it a try!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/8d83e9a0b06a80d6c4685b8a2f83de5d.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/8d83e9a0b06a80d6c4685b8a2f83de5d.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/8d83e9a0b06a80d6c4685b8a2f83de5d.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In our 2D platformer game, players take on the role of a brave rooster on a mission to rescue chickens that have been kidnapped by a sly fox and hidden in various locations. Players must use their wits and platforming skills to overcome challenging obstacles, outsmart the fox's traps, and save the chickens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/9e0605656b89905ca17f7a7fb3176ba5.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/9e0605656b89905ca17f7a7fb3176ba5.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/9e0605656b89905ca17f7a7fb3176ba5.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With pixel graphics and a retro aesthetic, our game offers a unique blend of adventure, puzzle-solving, and action. Players will need quick reflexes and strategic thinking to survive the fox’s various traps and hazards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/a3e89ebe1bbfb425fdc8cb3d6f062048.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/a3e89ebe1bbfb425fdc8cb3d6f062048.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/a3e89ebe1bbfb425fdc8cb3d6f062048.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Filled with cute characters and challenging levels, our game is a must-play for fans of indie, adventure, and puzzle platformers. Whether you're a seasoned platformer veteran or a newcomer to the genre, you’ll find plenty of excitement and challenge in our game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/0c1e68f70b9a42c301c2a11493987426.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/0c1e68f70b9a42c301c2a11493987426.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/0c1e68f70b9a42c301c2a11493987426.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the rooster on his quest to save the chickens and prove that even the smallest hero can triumph against impossible odds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/f7439b856b0a0e070f1ae08af8f58a90.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/f7439b856b0a0e070f1ae08af8f58a90.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/f7439b856b0a0e070f1ae08af8f58a90.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Difficulty:</strong> This game will likely be challenging and require players to use their skills and strategies to overcome obstacles and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adventure:</strong> Players will embark on a thrilling adventure to rescue chickens and take down the sly fox.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzle:</strong> The game may contain puzzles that players must solve in order to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Action:</strong> Players will engage in fast-paced action, running, jumping, and fighting their way through the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Side Scroller:</strong> The game will have a side-scrolling format, with players moving from left to right across the screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro:</strong> The pixel art style of the game will give it a nostalgic, retro feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Platformer:</strong> The game is a platformer, with players jumping and running across platforms to reach their goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategy:</strong> Players will need to use strategy and planning to successfully rescue the chickens and defeat the fox's defenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge:</strong> The game will present a series of challenges that players must overcome in order to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jump:</strong> Players will need to jump to avoid obstacles and reach high platforms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run:</strong> Players will need to run quickly to escape from enemies and navigate through levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/c3dda2e125679347940a8804ac82dfe5.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/c3dda2e125679347940a8804ac82dfe5.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/c3dda2e125679347940a8804ac82dfe5.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once upon a time, in a far-off land, there was a brave rooster who lived on a farm with his flock of chickens. However, a sly fox began to steal the chickens one by one, whisking them away to hidden locations. Determined to rescue his chickens, the rooster embarked on a perilous journey to track down the fox. Along the way, the rooster discovered he had the ability to shoot fire from his beak, which he used to fight off the fox’s traps and free the chickens. Eventually, the rooster reached the fox’s stronghold and engaged in a fierce battle. Despite facing many challenges and obstacles, the rooster never lost hope and ultimately emerged victorious, defeating the fox and rescuing the last of his chickens. The rooster returned home a hero, and the chickens lived happily ever after, safe and sound thanks to their brave protector. The end.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2f84d95c09edc6f4d8cde3e850696bf0.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2f84d95c09edc6f4d8cde3e850696bf0.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2f84d95c09edc6f4d8cde3e850696bf0.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Developer Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a solo indie game developer, creating my first game, <i>Rooster Tale</i>, has been a challenging but incredibly rewarding experience. The game follows the adventures of a rooster as he navigates through various levels filled with obstacles and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/726117ed1a43f5f54b89d85b3cc06008.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/726117ed1a43f5f54b89d85b3cc06008.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/726117ed1a43f5f54b89d85b3cc06008.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I wanted the game to have a retro feel, so I chose pixel graphics and incorporated elements of adventure and puzzle platforming. Making the game challenging is also important to me, so I’ve spent a lot of time playtesting and fine-tuning the difficulty to get it just right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2298436ea6b8b19e7012a8ae3e789f07.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2298436ea6b8b19e7012a8ae3e789f07.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/2298436ea6b8b19e7012a8ae3e789f07.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The process of developing <i>Rooster Tale</i> has had its obstacles. There have been many late nights spent coding and troubleshooting, as well as moments of self-doubt where I questioned whether I could see the project through to the end. However, the sense of accomplishment I will feel when I finally finish and publish the game will be worth all the hard work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/4a3246e92be365d85af32e6ccc4c3a8d.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/4a3246e92be365d85af32e6ccc4c3a8d.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/4a3246e92be365d85af32e6ccc4c3a8d.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The process of developing <i>Rooster Tale</i> has had its obstacles. There have been many late nights spent coding and troubleshooting, as well as moments of self-doubt where I questioned whether I could see the project through to the end. However, the sense of accomplishment I will feel when I finally finish and publish the game will be worth all the hard work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/6b1b708856172f7ea2ec8a15aff570d6.poster.avif?t=1731677179\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/6b1b708856172f7ea2ec8a15aff570d6.webm?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/6b1b708856172f7ea2ec8a15aff570d6.mp4?t=1731677179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250780/extras/ad438895147abe6b756d5542319ed